        {
          kind: 'commentary',
          id: 'heb12-asaleutos',
          html:
            'The kingdom you are receiving is not made by human hands. It is not subject to political change, economic collapse, or the shifting opinions of nations. It cannot be shaken. It is <em>asaleutos</em>—immovable, unshakeable, stable forever. Everything else—every empire, every system, every certainty the world promises—will eventually fall. Only God&apos;s kingdom remains.',
